VMaster PDF Editor is a free tool for personal use on Linux systems, it is not open source, but is an option to consider for the tasks involving editing and modifying pdf files. It is a complete solution for creating and editing both PDF and XPS files, and lets you add content to existing PDF <a class="excerpt-more" href="http://linuxaria.com/pills/master-pdf-editor-a-complete-tool-to-create-and-modify-pdf-files-with-linux?lang=en">[...]</a><div class="yarpp-related-rss yarpp-related-none">\u000a\u000aNo related posts.\u000a<img src="http://yarpp.org/pixels/ba2be3fba9b21a2a23229e17892b86c0" />\u000a</div>
